w) to start a fresh session, or use a larger-context model.","consecutiveErrors":1,"consecutiveSkipped":0}},{"id":"dde46f87-45b0-4c74-bad0-88c500754a92","name":"TK选品-泰国黑马-v7.0","enabled":false,"createdAtMs":1780989664430,"updatedAtMs":1780990214327,"agentId":"tts","schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 9,12,15,18,21 * * *","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"执行v7.0选品流程（泰国市场）\n\n## 第一步：Shopee 产品扫描\n用 curl 直调 Sorftime API，搜索泰国发饰品类（nodeId=11046516）：\n\n```bash\ncurl -s -X POST 'https://mcp.sorftime.com/' \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $(cat /tmp/sorftime_key.txt)\" \\\n  -H 'accept: application/json, text/event-stream' \\\n  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \\\n  -d '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"tools/call\",\"params\":{\"name\":\"shopee_product_search\",\"arguments\":{\"site\":\"TH\",\"nodeId\":\"11046516\",\"monthSaleVolumeRangeMin\":50,\"priceRangeMin\":50,\"page\":1}},\"id\":1}'\n```\n\n**通过条件（全部满足）：**\n- 月销量 ≥ 50单\n- 7天销量 ≥ 月销量×15%\n- 评分 ≥ 4.0\n- 上架时间 ≤ 6个月\n- 好评率 ≥ 90%\n\n**重点加分：MonthlySalesGrowth ≥ 30% 或 7天销量 ≥ 500**\n\n## 第二步：TikTok 趋势验证\n用 tiktok_similar_product 搜 Shopee 标题关键词，验证 TikTok 上有同款在卖。\n\n## 第三步：1688 利润终选\n用 ali1688_similar_product 查货源：\n\n毛利率公式（泰国）：毛利率 = 售价×52% - 1688价×汇率/售价\n泰国固定成本 ≈ 48%（平台26%+物流12%+仓储5%+退货5%），汇率1CNY≈5 THB\n\n**通过条件：1688采购价 ≤ ¥5 且 毛利率 ≥ 50%**\n（泰国市场竞争更激烈，建议毛利率门槛略高于越南）\n\n## 第四步：写入飞书多维表格\napp_token: AKppbAeyXanToTsVl6ScxO5QnZd\ntable_id: tblHU2do30jzinJT\n20个字段全填，不留空\n站点标注：泰国\n\n## 第五步：发送飞书选品报告\n包含：通过数量、等级分布（S/A/B/C）、核心爆款信息","timeoutSeconds":600},"delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"feishu","accountId":"tts"},"state":{}}],"total":2,"offset":0,"limit":2,"hasMore":false,"nextOffset":null,"deliveryPreviews":{"6ee6a981-7b1c-4560-a848-139401e7bfa6":{"label":"announce -> feishu:ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68","detail":"explicit"},"dde46f87-45b0-4c74-bad0-88c500754a92":{"label":"announce -> feishu:ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68","detail":"explicit"}}